      "id": "PopularPost324434",
      "post_content": "This card is beautiful in creature-sparse decks with countermagic and/or discard, but also in creature strategies with \"enter the battlefield\" effects, such as Ninjitsu and Haste. Echo cards like [Avalanche Riders](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Avalanche Riders) can also get ugly quickly with the assistance of this card.",
      "posted_by": "Equinox523",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost324434\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">This card is beautiful in creature-sparse decks with countermagic and/or discard, but also in creature strategies with \"enter the battlefield\" effects, such as Ninjitsu and Haste.  Echo cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Avalanche Riders\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Avalanche Riders\">Avalanche Riders</a> can also get ugly quickly with the assistance of this card.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '324434'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy1136\">Equinox523</span>\r\n                                (6/27/2013 6:26:38 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"